OL,7,FA dad experienced a "moment of
OL,8,Fmadness" at work which has landed him
OL,9,Fin prison, a court has heard.
OL,11,FSteven Finnigan was employed by Serco
OL,12,Fto perform checks on accommodation in
OL,13,FSt Helens which had been provided to
OL,14,Fasylum seekers.
OL,16,FBut he instead seized upon the
OL,17,Fopportunity to steal cash from one
OL,18,Fresident's bedroom.
