OL,7,FHe was caught red-handed after his
OL,8,Fvictim became suspicious of his
OL,9,Fpossessions going missing and set up a
OL,10,FRing doorbell camera in order to get
OL,11,Fto the bottom of the mystery.
OL,13,FLiverpool Crown Court heard yesterday,
OL,14,FMonday, that Abdulrahmen Hassouna left
OL,15,Fthe house in multiple occupation on
OL,16,FMorley Street in St Helens where he
OL,17,Flived on January 21 last year in order
OL,18,Fto volunteer at an asylum cafe.
