OL,7,FHowever, while he was away, the camera
OL,8,Fhe had set up in his room following
OL,9,Fearlier thefts of his belongings
OL,10,Fcaptured Finnigan, whose employer
OL,11,FSerco was contracted to maintain the
OL,12,Faccommodation, entering and rifling
OL,13,Fthrough his wardrobe before leaving in
OL,14,Fpossession of an item.
