OL,7,FEmily Land, prosecuting, described how
OL,8,FMr Hassouna later discovered that
OL,9,Faround #5 to #15 in cash was missing
OL,10,Ffrom his wallet, as was a quantity of
OL,11,FQatari currency. However, the 36-year-
OL,12,Fold defendant, of York Road in Huyton,
OL,13,Fdenied any wrongdoing and maintained
OL,14,Fhe had been visiting the bedroom as
OL,15,Fpart of his usual duties.
