OL,7,FIn a statement read to the court on
OL,8,Fhis behalf, Mr Hassouna said: "From
OL,9,Fthe time of reporting this incident,
OL,10,FI've been extremely stressed about
OL,11,Fwhat may happen. I'm concerned about
OL,12,Frepercussions. I'm worried that other
OL,13,Femployees may do something to me.
OL,15,F"I'm constantly anxious about who is
OL,16,Fknocking at the door. It wasn't safe
OL,17,Ffor us in Egypt. I wanted a new life
OL,18,Fin the UK. Now I don't feel safe here."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/14
