OL,7,FFinnigan has four previous convictions
OL,8,Ffor four offences, being fined for
OL,9,Fdrug driving in 2021 and threatening
OL,10,Fbehaviour in 2024. James Lefroy,
OL,11,Fdefending, told the court: "He is very
OL,12,Faccepting of the jury's verdict.
OL,14,F"He is accepting of the fact that your
OL,15,Fhonour must sentence him for this
OL,16,Foffence. He has not complained to me
OL,17,Fabout the system or the unfairness of
OL,18,Fthe system. He has been quiet and
OL,19,Frespectful of the court process.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/14
