OL,7,F"That is indicative of him and his
OL,8,Fbehaviour as a whole. I wish to frame
OL,9,Fthis as something that must have been
OL,10,Fa moment of madness. Mr Finnigan was
OL,11,Fin this job independently for a number
OL,12,Fof weeks. He had been employed in
OL,13,Fsimilar roles for months before that.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/14
