OL,7,F"Throughout his working relationship
OL,8,Fwith Serco, there were no other
OL,9,Fcomplaints whatsoever. This was
OL,10,Fsomething that was impulsive,
OL,11,Fsomething that he did not do on daily
OL,12,Fbasis and, for some reason, he took
OL,13,Fthe stupid decision to do something on
OL,14,Fthis occasion.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/14
