OL,7,F"He does have borderline personality
OL,8,Fdisorder. It is to such an extent that
OL,9,Fhis father lives with him to care for
OL,10,Fhim on a day to day basis. He has two
OL,11,Fchildren. He is estranged from their
OL,12,Fmother. They maintain a positive
OL,13,Frelationship for the purposes of their
OL,14,Fchildren, perhaps indicative of the
OL,15,Fkind of man that he is."
OL,17,FFinnigan was found guilty of one count
OL,18,Fof burglary following a trial.
OL,19,FAppearing in the dock wearing a khaki
OL,20,Fgreen Under Armour tracksuit top, he
OL,21,Fwas jailed for 12 months.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/14
