OL,7,FHaving turned to the public gallery
OL,8,Fand said "see you later" as he was led
OL,9,Fto the cells, one of his supporters
OL,10,Fwas heard to moan "f***ing b*****ks"
OL,11,Fas he left the courtroom.
OL,13,FSentencing, Judge Louise Brandon said:
OL,14,F"Mr Hassouna became increasingly
OL,15,Fconcerned that people were entering
OL,16,Fhis room and items of his property
OL,17,Fwere going missing. You conducted an
OL,18,Funexpected search of his room.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/14
