OL,7,F"On entering the room, you searched
OL,8,Fthrough the cupboard and pockets of
OL,9,Fthe jackets of the complainant. While
OL,10,Fyou were entitled to conduct searches,
OL,11,Fthe way in which you did it was not
OL,12,Fappropriate. You denied taking
OL,13,Fanything and maintained that you had
OL,14,Facted within the parameters of your
OL,15,Frole.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/14
