OL,7,F"You have no relevant previous
OL,8,Fconvictions. There has been no
OL,9,Fsuggestion of any further offending.
OL,10,FYou have contact with your children
OL,11,Fand have maintained a positive
OL,12,Frelationship with their mum. You have
OL,13,Fongoing mental and physical health
OL,14,Fchallenges.
OL,16,F"While I note your difficult
OL,17,Fupbringing, I cannot ignore that fact
OL,18,Fthat you had secured work with Serco
OL,19,Fand had an opportunity to make a good
OL,20,Ffuture for yourself."
